I would like to query using the features of the WAS ... DURING query, but would like to use sprints or sprint functions instead of the time range that DURING request.  For example:

{{status WAS "Resolved" BY jsmith DURING "Sprint A"}}
or
{{status WAS "Resolved" BY jsmith DURING openSprints()}}

